OK then, that’s it for today’s episode on Eli Cohen, the Israeli spy

00:25:15.996 --> 00:25:19.896
who infiltrated the upper-echelons of Syria's military establishment

00:25:20.056 --> 00:25:23.886
and just perhaps altered the course of Middle Eastern history.

